<i>noun</i>: 르포 [] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>르포 []</dt><br>
<dd>reportage</dd><br>
<dd>사건 현장에서 직접 하는 보도나 현장을 직접 보고 쓴 기사.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of reporting news right on the scene of an incident, or an article written after direct observation of the scene.</dd><br>
